{"tid":1702820,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家覺得雙11三罷，黃店到底應該開門幫手足定罷市？","createTime":"2019-11-10T02:45:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T10:56:09.000Z","uid":50762,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1b3224d698e0128cd5199eb291b43d499c9e8d65","tid":1702820,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:45:10.000Z","msg":"黃店應該支持三罷，一同罷市，否則以後唔當黃店？至少優先懲罰有真正罷工罷市既黃店先<br />\n<br />\n定<br />\n<br />\n黃店都照開門，有咩事支援手足？<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家到底點睇？<br />\n講真我就覺得打遊擊，唔需要幾多支援，相反黃店應該一齊罷，話俾政府聽我地既憤怒。<br />\n唔該手足今日就買好需要物資，聽日帶乾糧同水，唔好幫襯街上任何店，你三罷，但當普通行街照食野買野係無意思，行多幾步，做多幾下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOzrbAo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOzrbAo.jpg&h=ecaa564d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f8pyA14.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff8pyA14.jpg&h=944b460f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEYGKVp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEYGKVp.jpg&h=e9a29b77&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TcqU4Vq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTcqU4Vq.jpg&h=6e8c7183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3214e2fe2c4db6ecc236502bb014b3b6793f13cf","tid":1702820,"uid":50762,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:48:19.000Z","msg":"如果大家覺得應該罷市，唔該就咪再幫襯啲唔三罷既店。<br />\n尤其宜家愈來愈多藍扮黃，優先懲罰真黃店先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07f8e68d6e9216de4ff49adb94cd6a174d2868a6","tid":1702820,"uid":50762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:51:30.000Z","msg":"有無人有意見？以雙11決定懲罰力度"},{"pid":"b05b5a12031f90298e28226ef52efa7c90dc25c8","tid":1702820,"uid":50762,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T02:59:07.000Z","msg":"以後優先懲罰雙11罷市真黃店"},{"pid":"26b254b0b117eb48accd6be5c55a5eb88f809c6a","tid":1702820,"uid":157938,"like":1,"dislike":